definition.value: A derivative of L-gulonic acid having a keto group at the 3-position.
A scyllo-inositol phosphate having the phosphate at the 4-position and a guanidino group in place of the hydroxyl at position 1.
A trivalent inorganic anion obtained by removal of all three protons from selenophosphoric acid.
A monocarboxylic acid anion that is the conjugate base of maleamic acid.
